article_title: Sundance Quick Quote: Margot Robbie on her career success
article_text:
Topics: From the Wires, Entertainment News, News

PARK CITY, Utah (AP) — “Yeah. I’m still pinching myself. I’m pinching myself I’m here tonight I just – it’s all surreal. I don’t know why this is all happening but I’m really grateful it is.”

—Margot Robbie discussing her career at the premiere of “Z is for Zachariah” at Sundance

____

—Alicia Rancilio, www.twitter.com/aliciar
